    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "5. Then went out to him Jerusalem, and all Judea, and all the region round about Jordan—From the metropolitan center to the extremities of the Judean province the cry of this great preacher of repentance and herald of the approaching Messiah brought trooping penitents and eager expectants.",
        "children": []
