      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "1. If it be true, that from Ezra’s time till now no prophet had appeared. Our Saviour speaking of John, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "What went ye out for",
