        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "to see? A prophet?",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Seems to hint that a prophet was a great rarity amongst them. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
