          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "4. Especially if we consider the new rite of baptizing, which he brought in. For admit their washing of proselytes in use before, yet he baptized Jews. He was ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "sent to baptize with water, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "John 1:33",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "John 1:33",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". So as from this time the institution of the sacrament of baptism must be dated, and he did baptize many. ",
        "children": []
